# Organization configuration for {{_organizationName.title}}
Infrastructure-as-code for {{_organizationName.title}}'s teams and people.

## To run
```
yarn install
yarn build
AWS_ACCESS_KEY={key} AWS_SECRET_KEY={secret} yarn synth
cd cdktf.out
terraform init
TF_WORKSPACE=prod terraform plan -out=prod.tfplan
terraform apply prod.tfplan
```

## Bootstrapping
* Define your `SkepStack` in [src/stack.ts](./src/stack.ts). This will include:
  * Adding plugins to `deps` in `.projenrc.ts` for any necessary integrations, re-running `npx projen`.
  * Adding any necessary [Integrations](./src/stack.ts#L16) to the definition.
  * Adding [loading code](./src/stack.ts#L42-L50) for those integrations.
  * Adding all provider variables for those integrations to `.projenrc.ts`, re-running `npx projen`.
  * Adding GitHub secrets to the repo for all provider variables defined above.
* Add [person config](./src/config/people) for each person in the org; make sure to add them to [index.ts](./src/config/people/index.ts).
* Add [team config](./src/config/teams) for each team in the org; make sure to add them to [index.ts](./src/config/teams/index.ts).
* Delete this section when complete.
